name: Just the Tip
description: Just the tip... of what? My tongue? My knife? My strap? // I originally took this photo in March 2021 for a NSFW NFT platform that was supposed to be for sex workers, but turned out to not really be *FOR* us (like most of them are not), so I immediately burned it. Here it is again, 5 months later. Censored with Bitcoin lasers, of course. Model is me, Cryptonatrix. Self-photographed.
